Abstract = {The contextual information of multi-turn dialogue tasks is always
   overlooked in the modeling process, and the historical information of
   system responses are greatly challenged. In this paper, we explore the
   necessity of topic coherence in multi-turn conversations, and propose a
   deep hierarchical neural model within the RAG framework, modeling topic
