   Technology},
Abstract = {Our study proposes an intelligent teaching method based on RAG, which
   dynamically integrates authoritative knowledge bases with language
   models to address the limitations of large models in factual accuracy
   and domain-specific expertise. The experiments employ three evaluation
   metrics to validate the effectiveness of RAG in educational scenarios.
   The results demonstrate that the RAG-enhanced model (54.8\% accuracy)
   significantly outperforms baseline models (Llama2-7B at 38.8\%), and
   ablation studies confirm the critical role of the retrieval module and
   factual verification in performance improvement. The system supports
   personalized teaching resource generation, offering a new paradigm for
   AI-driven education.},
