Abstract = {Health literacy empowers people to access, understand and apply health
   information to effectively manage their own health and to be an active
   participant in healthcare decisions. In this paper we propose a
   conceptual model for cognitive factors affecting health literacy and
   related socioeconomic aspects. Then we develop the HEALIE Knowledge
